OL,3,CCouncil worker 'stole from the people
OL,4,Cof this city' in #40,000 plot
OL,6,FA council worker stole almost #40,000
OL,7,Ffrom taxpayers by issuing himself
OL,8,Ffraudulent refunds using council
OL,9,Fcredit card machines.
OL,11,FJames Owen, 36, used Liverpool City
OL,12,FCouncil's PDQ (process data quickly)
OL,13,Fmachines to transfer thousands of
OL,14,Fpounds into his personal bank account
OL,15,Falongside his salary.
