OL,3,CCouncil worker 'stole from the people
OL,4,Cof this city' in #40,000 plot
OL,6,FHe worked for the council between
OL,7,FApril 2019 and September 2024 in its
OL,8,Fmarket services department before an
OL,9,Finternal review in 2024 uncovered
OL,10,Ffinancial irregularities linked to the
OL,11,FPDQ machines.
OL,13,FBetween 3 October 2023 and 6 August
OL,14,F2024, #34,725 was paid out across 299
OL,15,Frefund transactions, some worth up to
OL,16,F#700.
OL,18,FA further #5,248 was refunded between
OL,19,F10 August and 5 September 2024 across
OL,20,F42 transactions.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/7
