OL,3,CCouncil worker 'stole from the people
OL,4,Cof this city' in #40,000 plot
OL,6,FIn total, #39,973 of council funds was
OL,7,Ffraudulently taken. Both bank cards
OL,8,Fused were linked to Owen's account.
OL,10,FBank statements later showed "every
OL,11,Frefund transaction was present in his
OL,12,Fbank account, in addition to the
OL,13,Fsalary he was receiving".
OL,15,FOn Wednesday 14 January, Owen, of
OL,16,FArden in Widnes, who pleaded guilty to
OL,17,Ffraud by abuse of position Liverpool
OL,18,FCrown Court, was sentenced.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
