OL,3,CCouncil worker 'stole from the people
OL,4,Cof this city' in #40,000 plot
OL,6,F"The one positive point was that he
OL,7,Fvoluntarily desisted. He walked out,
OL,8,Funable to cope with the pressure and
OL,9,Fguilt.
OL,11,F"On a positive note, he has somewhat
OL,12,Fpulled himself together, moved in with
OL,13,Fhis father, ceased drinking to excess.
OL,15,F"He's described as a low risk of
OL,16,Freoffending and low risk of serious
OL,17,Fharm. The message of the pre-sentence
OL,18,Freport is that he's a good candidate
OL,19,Ffor rehabilitation."
