OL,6,FPassing his sentencing, Judge Simon
OL,7,FMedland said: "You were in a good job
OL,8,Fwhich many people would have wanted,
OL,9,Fand for a period of time you enacted
OL,10,Fthat properly.
OL,12,F"But you began to drink heavily and
OL,13,Fyou began to take cocaine, which apart
OL,14,Ffrom destroyed your mental and
OL,15,Fphysical health and apart from being a
OL,16,Fserious controlled drug, is
OL,17,Fastonishingly expensive, and you began
OL,18,Fto thieve from the public, the people
OL,19,Fwho live in this city.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/7
