OL,3,CCouncil worker 'stole from the people
OL,4,Cof this city' in #40,000 plot
OL,6,F"You began to thieve from them and you
OL,7,Fcontinued to do until you had stolen
OL,8,Falmost #40,000 by making false,
OL,9,Fdishonest refunds."
OL,11,FOwen was sentenced to 16 months in
OL,12,Fprison, suspended for two years and
OL,13,Fwas ordered to complete 20
OL,14,Frehabilitation days and 200 hours of
OL,15,Funpaid work.
OL,17,FNo compensation order was made, but
OL,18,FLiverpool City Council will seek to
OL,19,Frecover the money through the civil
OL,20,Fcourts.
